name: Nemu Nadhi Resto
address: 6JR6+29V, br karang gede, Pejukutan, Kec. Nusa Penida, Kabupaten Klungkung, Bali 80771, Indonesia
review 1: Great food for reasonable prices, friendly staff, beautiful view on the ocean. Quality of food better than in Warungs on the beach. Had vegetatian curry there.
review 2: A lovely family-run restaurant with an incredible view of the ocean & the jungle. We had the chicken curry and vegetable curry which we watched Sri (the wonderful chef) cook from scratch. I also had the dragon fruit smoothie which was delicious. If you are looking for good, authentic Indonesian food with a local feel then try this place!
